#### PR description:

This PR updates the CRACK Phase-II setup by:
- correcting the local module-axis/orientation description in the geometry;
- updating the module positioning/range in the CRACK geometry files;
- updating the README with the recommended CMSSW setup;
- adding links to the DQM and packer/unpacker instructions.

Validation can be found in this [DPG-Presentation](https://indico.cern.ch/event/1628558/contributions/6877385/attachments/3202037/5700480/Phase2DPG-Meeting_16012026.pdf).
